        "created_at": "2018-06-19T08:29:40.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Just a borderline overripe wine that was better in its fleshy youth?</p>\n<p>Or a bottle in an awkward phase between youth and maturity?</p>\n<p>But once the alcohol starts to stick out, it seldom re-integrates.</p>",
